extends layout2
block content
  include carousel
  include section2
  .philosophy
    .container
      img(src="/img/bg-module-top-shadow.png")
      h1 Our Philosophy of Harmony between Machine and Support 
      .row
        .span10.offset1
          img.rb(src="/img/RB-icon.png")
          p.
            To serve our customers, we believe that a harmony must exist between 
            machine and support. A perfectly performing machine is not our end goal 
            because a machine without support does not create peace of mind. 
            Our desire is for you to feel a calm about any machine purchased from us.
            You will know that our ever present support is always there for you.
            This combination of the finest machines and superior support is 
            the rock upon which we build Rosito Bisani Imports. We are excited to serve
            you next.
